        <h2>üîß Troubleshooting</h2>
        
        <div class="troubleshooting-grid">
            <div class="trouble-item">
                <h3>‚ùå Bot Not Responding</h3>
                <div class="trouble-solutions">
                    <h4>Common Causes:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Bot lacks required permissions</li>
                        <li>Command used in restricted channel</li>
                        <li>Incorrect command syntax</li>
                        <li>Bot is offline or restarting</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Solutions:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Check bot permissions in server settings</li>
                        <li>Try the command in a different channel</li>
                        <li>Use <code>!bike help</code> for correct syntax</li>
                        <li>Check bot status at <a href="/bot-status">bot status page</a></li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="trouble-item">
                <h3>üè∑Ô∏è Auto-Roles Not Working</h3>
                <div class="trouble-solutions">
                    <h4>Common Causes:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Bot role is below target roles</li>
                        <li>Manage Roles permission missing</li>
                        <li>Auto-role feature disabled</li>
                        <li>Role hierarchy conflicts</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Solutions:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Move BikeNode bot role above target roles</li>
                        <li>Grant "Manage Roles" permission</li>
                        <li>Enable auto-roles: <code>!autorole enable</code></li>
                        <li>Check role configuration: <code>!autorole status</code></li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="trouble-item">
                <h3>üîç Search Results Empty</h3>
                <div class="trouble-solutions">
                    <h4>Common Causes:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Typo in bike name</li>
                        <li>Bike not in database</li>
                        <li>Search terms too specific</li>
                        <li>Database update in progress</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Solutions:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Check spelling and try variations</li>
                        <li>Use broader search terms</li>
                        <li>Try <code>!bike search [make]</code> first</li>
                        <li>Request bike addition via support</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="trouble-item">
                <h3>üìä Commands Slow or Timing Out</h3>
                <div class="trouble-solutions">
                    <h4>Common Causes:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>High server load</li>
                        <li>Database maintenance</li>
                        <li>Network connectivity issues</li>
                        <li>Large data requests</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Solutions:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Wait a moment and try again</li>
                        <li>Use more specific search terms</li>
                        <li>Check <a href="/status">service status page</a></li>
                        <li>Contact support if persistent</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
